measurements.description: A group of fourteen relatively uniform plants representing a charming combination of the two species parents; flower color ranges from pale pink to white on flowers resembling the medusa parent; parents are Habenaria carnea 'Winter Haven' and Habenaria medusa '#1', hybridizer Mike Dorris; Habenaria Pegasus 'Rick Stier' HCC/AOS, award 20185418, was awarded at this judging, Habenaria Pegasus 'Pat Wik-Stier' HCC/AOS, award 20174085, was previously awarded.
